GOLD

The official URL for this implementation guide is: 

https://www.vision-zero-oncology.de/fhir/ImplementationGuide/gold

Implementation Guide German Oncological Data Standard (GOLD)

title: German Oncological Data Standard (GOLD)

extension.valueMarkdown: Automatically added as a dependency - all IGs depend on HL7 Terminology

resource.name: Profile Body Height
resource.description: Profile for body height of a patient

resource.name: Profile Body Structure
resource.description: Profile for the base definition of all body structures.

resource.name: Profile Body Weight
resource.description: Profile for body weight of a patient

resource.name: Clinical Study
resource.description: This profile describes a clinical study in which a patient takes part.

resource.name: Profile ECOG Performance Status
resource.description: Profile for the Eastern Cooperative Oncology Group (ECOG) Performance Status that represents a cancer patient's functional status.

resource.name: Profile Histology Topography
resource.description: Profile for the classification of a tumor's morphology(histology) and topography using ICD-O-3.

resource.name: Profile Histopathological Tumor Grading WHO
resource.description: Profile for the description of a tumor's grade using the general four-tier grading scheme following the recommendations of the WHO classification of tumors and UICC.

resource.name: Profile Karnofsky Performance Status
resource.description: Profile for the Karnofsky Performance Status to measure a cancer patient's ability to perform ordinary tasks.

resource.name: ProbandIn
resource.description: Dieses Profil beschreibt eine Proband*in.

resource.name: Profile RECIST timepoint assessment response
resource.description:
Profile for the RECIST timepoint assessment response which is available for each assessment timepoint as published here: https://recist.eortc.org/recist-1-1-2/
Please note there is no assessment timepoint response for the baseline assessment.

resource.name: Tumor
resource.description: Tumor

resource.name: Tumor Disorder
resource.description: Profile for a tumor disorder

resource.name: Tumor Specimen
resource.description: Tumor specimen

resource.name: Profile UICC TNM
resource.description: Profile for the tumor classification using TNM stage groups (I, II, III, or IV) and TNM staging elements (T, N, and M).

resource.name: Profile UICC TNM Residual Tumor (R) Classification
resource.description: Profile for the residual tumor (R) classification as part of TNM.

resource.name: Profile Vital Signs Base
resource.description: Profile for the base definition of all vital signs. May not be used directly. Only for reprofiling purposes.

resource.name: Diagnosesicherung ICD O
resource.description: Extension für die Erfassung der Diagnosesicherung der ICD-O-3

resource.name: Diagnosis
resource.description: Enables to reference a diagnosis <Condition> the body stucture refers to

resource.name: Specimen part of Tumor
resource.description: Enables to reference a Tumor <BodyStructure> from its respective Specimen

resource.name: Extension UICC TNM Prefix CPU
resource.description: The Extension allows to add c, p and u prefixes to TNM stages.

resource.name: Extension UICC TNM Suffix ITC
resource.description: The Extension allows to add isolated tumor cells (ITC) suffixes to the N- and M-categories in TNM.

resource.name: Extension UICC TNM Suffix ITC SN
resource.description: The Extension allows to add isolated tumor cells (ITC) sentinel lymph nodes (sn) suffix to the N-category in TNM.

resource.name: Diagnosesicherung ICD-O-3
resource.description: ValueSet für die Diagnosesicherungscodes der ICD-O-3

resource.name: recist-timepoint-response-vs
resource.description: Defines the valid values for the recist assessment response observation resource

resource.name: ValueSet ECOG Performance Status SNOMED
resource.description: The ValueSet contains the ECOG Performance Status values from SNOMED CT.

resource.name: ValueSet Histologic Grade SNOMED
resource.description: The ValueSet contains codes for the tumor grading system following the recommendations of the WHO Classification of Tumors from SNOMED CT.

resource.name: ValueSet Morphology ICD-O-3
resource.description: The ValueSet contains the morphology (histology) codes from ICD-O-3.

resource.name: ValueSet Morphology SNOMED
resource.description: The ValueSet contains the morphology (histology) codes from SNOMED CT.

resource.name: ValueSet Studiendesign NCIt
resource.description: Studiendesign aus NCI Thesaurus (NCIt)

resource.name: ValueSet Studienkategorien NCIt
resource.description: Studienkategorien aus NCI Thesaurus (NCIt)

resource.name: ValueSet Study Focus NCIt
resource.description: Study Focus aus NCI Thesaurus (NCIt)

resource.name: ValueSet TNM Classification Type LOINC
resource.description: This ValueSet contains codes to specifiy the type of TNM classification as clinical (cTNM) or pathological (pTNM).

resource.name: ValueSet TNM L-Descriptor Lymphatic Invasion UICC
resource.description: This ValueSet contains the TNM degree of lymphatic invasion codes used with the L-descriptor from TNM 8th edition UICC.

resource.name: ValueSet TNM M Category UICC
resource.description: This ValueSet contains the TNM M category codes from TNM 8th edition UICC.

resource.name: ValueSet TNM M Staging Type LOINC
resource.description: This ValueSet contains codes to specifiy the TNM distant metastases (M) category as clinical (cM) or pathological (pM).

resource.name: ValueSet TNM N Category UICC
resource.description: This ValueSet contains the TNM N category codes from TNM 8th edition UICC.

resource.name: ValueSet TNM N Staging Type LOINC
resource.description: This ValueSet contains codes to specifiy the TNM regional lymph nodes (N) category as clinical (cN) or pathological (pN).

resource.name: ValueSet TNM Pn-Descriptor Perineural Invasion UICC
resource.description: This ValueSet contains the TNM degree of perineural (lymphatic nerve sheet) invasion codes used with the Pn-descriptor from TNM 8th edition UICC.

resource.name: ValueSet TNM Prefix CPU UICC
resource.description: This ValueSet contains the c, p and u prefixes for TNM stages from TNM 8th edition UICC.

resource.name: ValueSet TNM Residual Tumor (R) Classification UICC
resource.description: This ValueSet contains the TNM residual tumor (R) classification codes from TNM 8th edition UICC.

resource.name: ValueSet TNM S Serum Tumour Markers UICC
resource.description: This ValueSet contains the TNM serum levels of tumor markers coded for germ cell tumors used with the S-symbol from TNM 8th edition UICC.

resource.name: ValueSet TNM Stage Group UICC
resource.description: The ValueSet contains codes for the TNM stage groups ranging from I to IV to group cancer patients with similar prognosis from TNM 8th edition UICC.

resource.name: ValueSet TNM Suffix ITC SN UICC
resource.description: This ValueSet contains the isolated tumor cells (ITC) sentinel lymph nodes (sn) suffix for the N-category in TNM from TNM 8th edition UICC.

resource.name: ValueSet TNM Suffix ITC UICC
resource.description: This ValueSet contains the isolated tumor cells (ITC) suffixes for N- and M-category from TNM 8th edition UICC.

resource.name: ValueSet TNM T Category UICC
resource.description: This ValueSet contains the TNM T category codes from TNM 8th edition UICC.

resource.name: ValueSet TNM T Multiplicity UICC
resource.description: This ValueSet contains the TNM primary tumor multiplicity codes used with the m-symbol from TNM 8th edition UICC.

resource.name: ValueSet TNM T Staging Type LOINC
resource.description: This ValueSet contains codes to specifiy the TNM primary tumor (T) category as clinical (cT) or pathological (pT).

resource.name: ValueSet TNM V-Descriptor Venous Invasion UICC
resource.description: This ValueSet contains the TNM degree of venous invasion codes used with the V-descriptor from TNM 8th edition UICC.

resource.name: ValueSet Topography ICD-O-3
resource.description: The ValueSet contains the topography codes from ICD-O-3.

resource.name: ValueSet Topography SNOMED
resource.description: The ValueSet contains the topography codes from SNOMED CT.

resource.description: Type of Blinding aus NCI Thesaurus (NCIt)

resource.description: Type of Randomization aus NCI Thesaurus (NCIt)
